{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place bread, onion and salt into mixing bowl and chop <b>Turbo\/2 sec\/2 times<b> until fine crumbs form. Transfer to a bowl and set aside.","Place 2 oz butter into mixing bowl and heat <b>1 min\/195°F\/speed 1<b>.","Add mushrooms and chop <b>5 sec\/speed 5<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula and cook <b>5 min\/195°F\/speed 1<b>.","Add reserved bread crumb mixture and stir <b>10 sec\/speed 3<b>, scrape down sides of mixing bowl. Set mixing bowl aside and allow to cool 15 minutes.","Add cream cheese, nutmeg, lemon juice, pepper and remaining 2 oz butter and blend <b>20 sec\/speed 5<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl and lid with spatula.","Add parsley, and blend <b>20 sec\/speed 5<b>. Transfer to a bowl, cover with cling wrap and refrigerate for at least 1 hour. Serve chilled."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["1 oz stale bread, roughly torn","½ oz onion","½ - 1 tsp salt","4 oz salted butter, softened, divided","9 oz fresh mushrooms (e.g. crimini or portobello), quartered","3 ½ oz cream cheese","½ tsp fresh ground nutmeg","1 tsp lemon juice","½ tsp ground black pepper","3 sprigs fresh parsley, leaves only"]}],"id":"r106931","imageLink":"https:\/\/3.bp.blogspot.com\/-UEMNGAOZYYM\/XZafMN24t5I\/AAAAAAAAgsE\/0g6RPjPT5Is0bdE7yi1FLDhcYVsZL0mFQCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_jIQK7pHM7iDq9kqW.png","title":"Mushroom Pâté","publishedAt":"2017-03-17T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"3 g","fat":"18 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"4 g","calories":"757 kJ \/ 181 kcal"},"usefulItems":"cling wrap, refrigerator","hintsAndTricks":["Use 1 oz bread crumbs to replace stale bread, if unavailable."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","1h 30m","1"]}